<div class="tab-pane fade" id="questions">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span7">
      <label><strong>Briefly share how you will add up to your community</strong></label>
      <%= f.text_field :cause ,  :class => "input-xxlarge", :placeholder => "I will add up by…(20 word maximum)" %>
      <div class ="controls">
        <label><strong>Your sponsor for the community service project* </strong> </label>
        <span class="help-block">Name, title, e-mail and quote from a person from the organization / person that will be benefitted by your project or who knows you and your project firsthand.</span>
        <div class="controls controls-row" >
          <%= f.text_field :name_sponsor , :class => "input-large", :placeholder => "Name*"%>
          <%= f.text_field :job, :class => "span2", :placeholder => "Title*" %>
          <%= f.text_field :email_sponsor, :class  => "input-large", :placeholder => "E-mail" %>
        </div>
        <%= f.text_field :quote, :class => "input-xxlarge", :placeholder => "Quote*" %>
      </div>
      <label><strong>About me and my educational goals...</strong>
        <%= f.text_area :answer1 , :rows => 10,  :class => "input-xxlarge", :placeholder => "max 800 characters" %>
      </label>
      <label><strong>Why I care about adding...</strong>
        <%= f.text_area :answer2 , :rows => 10, :class => "input-xxlarge", :placeholder => "max 800 characters" %>
      </label>
    </div>

    <div class="span5">
        <i class="icon-hand-right"></i><strong>&nbsp;Ideas of social community projects</strong>
     <!-- Accordion -->
      <div id="accordion2" class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-group">
          <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a href="#collapseOne" data-parent="#accordion2" data-toggle="collapse" class="accordion-toggle">Short on Time? Do it Online!</a>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body collapse" id="collapseOne">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <ul>
                <li>Subtitles for<a data-original-title="Visit Official Site" href="http://www.khanacademy.org/contribute" rel="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" target="_blank" id="tooltip"> Kahn Academy Videos </a>Create an online pledge or petition for your social cause. (i.e Stop Bullying:Speak Up at Facebook)</li>
                <li>Commit to use social network to promote your social cause via daily, weekly or monthly posts.</li>
                <li>Start a social media campaign for your cause.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-group">
          <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a href="#collapseTwo" data-parent="#accordion2" data-toggle="collapse" class="accordion-toggle">Feeling Creative? </a>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body collapse" id="collapseTwo">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <ul>
                <li> Donate a work of art of your creation to a children's hospital, adult care center, etc.</li>
                <li>Share your musical abilities by offering one or more free concerts in a low resource community, adult
                  care center, children hospital, etc.</li>
                <li>Design free logos for charitable on-campus organizations</li>
                <li>Write a song and create a music video to promote a social cause and share it on You Tube</li>
                <li>Write and publish an article in a local newspaper, magazine or internet blog promoting a social cause.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-group">
          <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a href="#collapseThree" data-parent="#accordion2" data-toggle="collapse" class="accordion-toggle">Cultural &amp; Religious Focus?</a>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body collapse" id="collapseThree">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <ul>
                <li>Organize monthly events to promote your country's culture, cuisine, art, movies and traditions.</li>
                <li>Organize monthly interfaith discussion groups to promote tolerance and understanding among
                  different faiths.</li>
                <li>Create an online community with your friends to promote faith and moral values.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-group">
          <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a href="#collapseFour" data-parent="#accordion2" data-toggle="collapse" class="accordion-toggle">Action Oriented? Volunteer your Time</a>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body collapse" id="collapseFour">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <ul>
                <li>Start a weekly literacy volunteer program at the local children´s cancer hospital</li>
                <li>Organize monthly visits to the local homeless shelter</li>
                <li>Volunteer once a week at the local soup kitchen</li>
                <li>Run a clothes / food / books drive for a community in need and organize a one day delivery event</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-group">
          <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a href="#collapseFive" data-parent="#accordion2" data-toggle="collapse" class="accordion-toggle">Career Focused?</a>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body collapse" id="collapseFive">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <ul>
                <li>Start an engineering club at your university to design and manufacture water filtering systems and
                  distribute them to poor communities</li>
                <li>Start an Operation Smile chapter at your university</li>
                <li>Create a marketing jingle for a charitable organization</li>
                <li>Elaborate a financial forecast for a charitable organization</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-group">
          <div class="accordion-heading">
            <a href="#collapseSix" data-parent="#accordion2" data-toggle="collapse" class="accordion-toggle">Free for the Summer?</a>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body collapse" id="collapseSix">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Spend your summer volunteering for a charitable cause or interning for a non profit organization.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div> <!-- Accordion -->

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
